  textLinkPrefab: {fileID: 0}
  render: {fileID: 251}
  Text: "                    How does this work?\r\n\r\n\u25CF Hosting a game gives
    you a game code \r\n    near the start button\r\n\u25CF Share the game code with
    friends to\r\n    create a private room.\r\n\u25CF Or tap \"Private\" to make
    the room\r public\n    for \"Find Game\"\r\n\u25CF The host can ban or kick players\r
    whenever\n    chat is available.\r\n\u25CF Still having problems?\r\n    Let us
    know on our Discord!"
